        <Parent_String>Lonicera (genus) [300375566], Caprifoliaceae (family) [300375567], Dipsacales (order) [300375568], Magnoliopsida (class) [300375593], Angiospermae (division) [300265706], Plantae (kingdom) [300132360], Eukaryota (domain) [300265677], living organisms (entities) [300390503], Living Organisms (hierarchy name) [300265673], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
